{"tid":476822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[封殺耶穌] 中國叫停梵蒂岡旅遊圖向教廷施壓","createTime":"2017-11-22T11:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T14:31:33.000Z","uid":43189,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"1d2238a86b564e6b3123e4565fa51e6bf49c0705","tid":476822,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:03:42.000Z","msg":"中梵關係一向若即若離，國家旅遊局日前突然向旅行社發出內部封殺令，禁止以梵蒂岡、帕勞等地作為旅遊目的地。並要求旅行社全部刪除梵蒂岡以及聖彼得大教堂旅遊宣傳。官方人士證實，該禁令緣於政治原因。（黃小山 / 林國立　報道）<br />\n<br />\n鳳凰假期國際旅行社本月16日發出的通知顯示，當局禁止旅行社組團前往梵蒂岡和西太平洋島國帕勞，違規旅行社將受嚴厲處罰。<br />\n<br />\n通知還稱，旅行社對行程中涉及梵蒂岡的景點，如聖彼得大教堂的圖文，必須全部刪除。並透露，已有同程、途牛等因為在旅遊產品推介中涉及上述目的地，已被處以30萬元的巨額罰款。而在此前，旅行社組團前往梵蒂岡旅遊則一直被官方默許。<br />\n<br />\n本台記者致電鳳凰假期國際旅行社北京辦公室，該公司人士表示，該通知來自國家旅遊局，並表示不方便回答問題。<br />\n<br />\n他說︰這個辦不了，現在梵蒂岡還沒有建交嘛。我還沒辦法回答你，這都是國家旅遊局定的。具體的這些都是官方給的一些政策，我們現在不方便回答。好吧？<br />\n<br />\n鳳凰假期成都分公司也證實，此前有的梵蒂岡景點，已經被叫停。但表示如果客戶需要，可以變通，但不保證一定成功。<br />\n<br />\n他說︰今後都不會有了，因為現在梵蒂岡嘛因為國際形勢的原因嘛，現在我們旅行社基本上都不含在裡面了。如果你這邊需要的話，我們可以看能給你安排一下，但是不保證一定給你包含在裡面。<br />\n<br />\n據稱已被國家旅遊局處罰的途牛國旅，回應查詢時亦表示，國家旅遊局不許進這個景點。<br />\n<br />\n她說︰之前有，但是現在沒有這條線路了。跟團是不進的，這景點。對，國家旅遊局下文不讓去那裡，這個沒有辦法的。從什麼時候開始是吧？嗯，這個我不太清楚。<br />\n<br />\n廣東省旅遊局一官員透露，該禁令來自國家層面，和前一段時間禁止去韓國旅遊一樣，都是因為政治原因。<br />\n<br />\n他說︰這種通知並不是我們發的，而是國家的。梵蒂岡它是教皇他統治的一個國家，他都沒有合法地承認我們。因為這個涉及到外交的，它這個只有外交部、國家旅遊局那邊才有這個資格，國家是有一定部署的，就好像之前不能去韓國一樣。國家它有個政治動態嘛，我們都不一定掌握。如果是通過旅行社的渠道的話，那旅行社肯定就不敢。因為它作為企業的話，不可能擔外交的風險跟責任嘛。一般來說的話海關可能也會有這個規定，你自行去的話如果海關抽查到還是不太好。要注意規避一下政治風險。<br />\n<br />\n本台記者致電國家旅遊局辦公室，但未獲直接回應。而國家旅遊咨詢熱線則回應稱，她沒有查到公開禁令。<br />\n<br />\n4年前，教宗方濟各成為羅馬教會的領袖後，力圖改善與中國的關係，並於去年開始與中國方面就主教任命等事宜進行談判。但迄今為止，因雙方存在較大分歧，談判未獲實質進展。<br />\n<br />\n中國與太平洋島國帕勞並無外交關係。帕勞自1999年起與台灣建交。<br />\n<br />\n帕勞近年成為最受中國遊客歡迎的目的地之一，遊客人數創下記錄，令當地資源和接待力量一直很緊張，備受挑戰。此外，當地居民也擔憂給環境帶來長遠影響，因帕勞的自然奇觀來自獨特的生態系統，遊客過多可能對當地自然景觀和野生動物的保護帶來威脅。為緩解壓力，帕勞已將來自中國的航班減半。<br />\n<br />\n帕勞政府強調並非歧視中國遊客，只是一些市場調整，避免當地旅遊市場太過依賴某個國家。<br />\n<br />\n近年來，中國多次利用叫停旅遊在內的經濟手段向有糾紛的國家施壓。今年3月韓國部署薩德反導系統時，中國國家旅遊局亦發出緊急通知，禁止旅行社組團前往韓國和日本旅遊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/catholic-11202017070611.html?encoding=traditional#.WhPFXZ4kc1Y.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fcatholic-11202017070611.html%3Fencoding%3Dtraditional%23.WhPFXZ4kc1Y.facebook&d=aJxo8tvkZ7gGKeC6DXYCFozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=07f6338e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/catholic-11202017070611.html?encoding=traditional#.WhPFXZ4kc1Y.facebook</a>"},{"pid":"cd55bfea934dbfbbc6d957f8aaba3ec9174d6caf","tid":476822,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:05:19.000Z","msg":"鎖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07d9cbc79fcdbffa530db89782b87eb9e2f57a3","tid":476822,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:25:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76f79751b884884c7630178436a6d0b61019e7fe","tid":476822,"uid":139349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:27:29.000Z","msg":"不信主的邪惡國度"},{"pid":"a096806f1d3f757fa6c42d599e0aeb5eeffb4b9b","tid":476822,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:33:42.000Z","msg":"耶穌都敢搞<br />\n仆街拿支共！"},{"pid":"2699c854625000140dceaa6499f4a9af0f728ea6","tid":476822,"uid":1977,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:34:26.000Z","msg":"大陸真係覺得佢d人唔去果度旅行就唔掂咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfa8984c51cd6c2019d9211aa254ff0cc77c225","tid":476822,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:36:38.000Z","msg":"呢個係魔鬼嘅考驗嚟"},{"pid":"ccd9676a4d912a1277701f4137062560421b3c6b","tid":476822,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:40:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b26f961bd21406b55a0b7bd7cf08508764b76039","tid":476822,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:46:11.000Z","msg":"唔想有事盡量唔好同中國做生意 <br />\n<br />\n賺到都隨時蝕突"},{"pid":"c28b2efaa3cf7b1073ee9bd04923dc595f21ec5f","tid":476822,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:46:11.000Z","msg":"唔想有事盡量唔好同中國做生意 <br />\n<br />\n賺到都隨時蝕突"},{"pid":"839053e38dd5c60a50b7227c4f43505f539011ad","tid":476822,"uid":2772,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸真係覺得佢d人唔去果度旅行就唔掂咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇大陸人既旅遊景點<br />\n反而係賣點"},{"pid":"fb8c60c22844977e8276d97a20ff2007beb00ebb","tid":476822,"uid":88250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:57:43.000Z","msg":"搞錯左，應該要求所有旅行社歐洲團都去梵蒂岡，咁先有阻嚇力"},{"pid":"42c296dba00ca2e6b80f418c1cb4c60bc8ac31d7","tid":476822,"uid":108685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大陸真係覺得佢d人唔去果度旅行就唔掂咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇大陸人既旅遊景點<br />\n反而係賣點</blockquote><br />\n上年去韓國濟州島一隻蝗都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n導遊都話當地班人就好大影響<br />\n但係今次人地係歐洲國家<br />\n主要遊客都係鬼佬 <br />\n反正人地咁細而且都唔想見到你班唔信天主教既蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc3a6ea6db35388b26d60da13a0f661292a5f5d","tid":476822,"uid":20241,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/200656_f35175ec6d282f804a18b9095d40d4ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F200656_f35175ec6d282f804a18b9095d40d4ee.jpg&h=aaf01239&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2dabb6ed889e2f2b9aca4ffe3c1b47063d61cebb","tid":476822,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:06:59.000Z","msg":"你拆完天主教基督教徒十字架<br />\n仲向教皇挑機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家天主教勢力認真廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368573ed330bab327f12beed331aa4db0f817536","tid":476822,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:13:23.000Z","msg":"沒有耶穌 你還有黨呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3d28a03475316f32cb6c262276431ff4fd9340","tid":476822,"uid":12370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:14:12.000Z","msg":"最好就係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暑假去一車車大陸人又唔係去朝聖或者欣賞建築去塞住曬坐係到"},{"pid":"be41b569c33469edcd59211c196546d861d891c7","tid":476822,"uid":61105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:15:39.000Z","msg":"人地又唔係等你個幾歐入場費開飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af96cb6a260537ed0a7d65da9dd6735494bbba4","tid":476822,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:19:55.000Z","msg":"支那畜以為自己乜料？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8cc55f10f58d06cd69a708272c9529bfc8a516a","tid":476822,"uid":108090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:20:00.000Z","msg":"事實上歐洲班商家不知幾恨中國人去旅遊<br />\n情況就如同香港商家一樣<br />\n連登仔無謂自欺欺人 講到歐佬唔自在咁"},{"pid":"32c94d97a32aa9c2b9890bbb1c51f46a2ca6ba9b","tid":476822,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:23:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事實上歐洲班商家不知幾恨中國人去旅遊<br />\n情況就如同香港商家一樣<br />\n連登仔無謂自欺欺人 講到歐佬唔自在咁</blockquote><br />\n如果教宗真係信耶穌，佢會寧願多啲人加入天主教會，多過想啲人去嗰到旅行。"},{"pid":"b6385dba1c2f0bfb51efc3a436eba339a64f9f2c","tid":476822,"uid":2140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:25:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事實上歐洲班商家不知幾恨中國人去旅遊<br />\n情況就如同香港商家一樣<br />\n連登仔無謂自欺欺人 講到歐佬唔自在咁</blockquote><br />\n你知唔知梵蒂岡係咩地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a9a5d3c73c90b1f41e42c20466346d0ea05c98","tid":476822,"uid":108090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:28:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>事實上歐洲班商家不知幾恨中國人去旅遊<br />\n情況就如同香港商家一樣<br />\n連登仔無謂自欺欺人 講到歐佬唔自在咁</blockquote><br />\n你知唔知梵蒂岡係咩地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梵蒂岡啲人吸仙氣維持生命？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4441160a323afc52fa3bbc1018615ee8fc4dc1a1","tid":476822,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:29:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>事實上歐洲班商家不知幾恨中國人去旅遊<br />\n情況就如同香港商家一樣<br />\n連登仔無謂自欺欺人 講到歐佬唔自在咁</blockquote><br />\n你知唔知梵蒂岡係咩地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梵蒂岡啲人吸仙氣維持生命？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n天主教會咁有錢，你大陸狗唔去嗰到旅行咁又點？"},{"pid":"764e23a8d4ab25595df7dfefae5aa7a9dde5deb1","tid":476822,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:30:09.000Z","msg":"上帝禁區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}